TITLE: Initializing Checkout SDK
DESCRIPTION: Async function to initialize the Checkout SDK, create a checkout service, and load the checkout with the current cart ID.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bigcommerce/docs/blob/main/docs/storefront/cart-checkout/checkout-sdk/index.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: html
CODE:
```
<script>
        const initSdk = async () => {
            window.module = await checkoutKitLoader.load('checkout-sdk');
            window.service = module.createCheckoutService();
            window.state = await service.loadCheckout('{{{ checkout.id }}}');
        };
        initSdk();
</script>
