TITLE: Adding a Billing Address to BigCommerce Checkout in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Helper function for adding a billing address to a checkout using the BigCommerce Storefront API. Requires the cart/checkout ID and address details to create or update the billing information.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bigcommerce/docs/blob/main/docs/storefront/cart-checkout/guide/rest-storefront.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function addBillingAddress(url, cartId, data) {
  return fetch(url + cartId + `/billing-address`,  {
    method: "POST",
    credentials: "same-origin",
    headers: {
      "Content-Type": "application/json",
    },
    body: JSON.stringify(data),
  })
  .then(response => response.json())
  .catch(error => console.error(error));
};
```

