TITLE: Response from Adding Consignment to Checkout
DESCRIPTION: This response shows the checkout object after adding a consignment. It includes the cart details, billing address, and the newly created consignment with shipping address and line item IDs.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bigcommerce/docs/blob/main/docs/storefront/headless/end-to-end-guides/rest-management.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_7

