TITLE: Resetting Customer Password using GraphQL Mutation
DESCRIPTION: This mutation completes the password reset process by accepting a new password along with the customer ID and reset token that were included in the reset password email link.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bigcommerce/docs/blob/main/docs/storefront/graphql/customers.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
mutation {
  customer {
    resetPassword(
      input: {
        customerEntityId: 1 # Provided in the link contained in the reset password email
        token: "" # Provided in the link contained in the reset password email
        newPassword: "NewPassword1234"
      }
    ) {
      errors {
        ... on ValidationError {
          message
        }
        ... on ChangePasswordError {
          message
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

