TITLE: Requesting Access Token for BigCommerce Single-Click App
DESCRIPTION: POST request to exchange the authorization code for an access_token. The request body combines query arguments from the auth callback with app credentials.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bigcommerce/docs/blob/main/docs/integrations/apps/guide/auth.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: http
