TITLE: Logging BODL Events to Browser Console
DESCRIPTION: A JavaScript script that subscribes to various BODL events and logs their payloads to the browser console. The script handles events for consent, products, banners, cart operations, and checkout processes. It includes validation for required BODL objects and initializes necessary data structures.
