TITLE: Querying Order Metafields with GraphQL
DESCRIPTION: This query retrieves metafields for order #102 using GraphQL. It uses entityId to filter for a specific order and returns both order metafields and cart metafields within a specified namespace.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bigcommerce/docs/blob/main/docs/storefront/graphql/orders.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
query Order($namespace: String!) {
    site {
        order(filter: {entityId: 102}) {
            id
            entityId
            billingAddress {
                firstName
            }
            metafields(namespace: $namespace) {
                edges {
                    node {
                        key
                        value
                    }
                }
            }
            cartMetafields(namespace: $namespace) {
                edges {
                     node {
                        key
                        value
                    }
                }
            }

        }
    }

}
```

