TITLE: Removing Product Custom Fields Overrides with GraphQL Mutation
DESCRIPTION: GraphQL mutation to remove custom field overrides for a specific channel locale. Takes product ID and context data as input parameters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bigcommerce/docs/blob/main/docs/store-operations/catalog/msf-international-enhancements/product-custom-fields.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
mutation ($input: RemoveProductCustomFieldsOverridesInput!) {
  product {
    removeProductCustomFieldsOverrides(input: $input) {
      product {
        customFields {
          edges {
            node {
              id
              name
              value
              overrides (context: { channelId: "bc/store/channel/1", locale: "en-US" }) {
                edges {
                  node {
                    ... on ProductCustomFieldOverridesForChannelLocale {
                      name
                      value
                      isVisible
                      context {
                        channelId
                        locale
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "input": {
    "productId": "bc/store/product/111",
    "data": [
      {
        "customFieldId": "bc/store/productCustomField/1",
        "channelLocaleContextData": {
          "context": {
            "channelId": "bc/store/channel/1",
            "locale": "en-US"
          },
          "attributes": ["NAME", "VALUE", "IS_VISIBLE"]
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

