LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
# Fetch product reviews for a product
query reviewsByProductId(
  $productId: Int!
  $cursor: String
  # Use GraphQL Query Variables to inject your product ID
) {
  site {
    product(entityId: $productId) {
      reviews(first:250, after:$cursor) {
        pageInfo {
          endCursor
          hasNextPage
        }
        edges {
          node {
            rating
            title
            text
            createdAt {
              utc
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
```

