TITLE: Setting Product Modifier Options with GraphQL in BigCommerce
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to set product modifier options using GraphQL mutations in BigCommerce. It allows setting options at the global level and for specific locales.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bigcommerce/docs/blob/main/docs/store-operations/catalog/msf-international-enhancements/product-modifier-options.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
mutation {
  catalog {
    setProductModifierOptions(
      input: {
        productId: "123"
        modifierOptions: [
          {
            id: "456"
            name: "Size"
            values: [
              { id: "789", label: "Small" }
              { id: "101", label: "Medium" }
              { id: "112", label: "Large" }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ) {
      product {
        entityId
        name
        modifierOptions {
          edges {
            node {
              entityId
              displayName
              values {
                edges {
                  node {
                    entityId
                    label
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

