TITLE: Querying Account Store Users with GraphQL in BigCommerce
DESCRIPTION: This GraphQL query retrieves detailed information about users associated with stores under a BigCommerce account. It includes user details such as ID, email, name, permissions, and associated apps.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bigcommerce/docs/blob/main/docs/graphql-account/users.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
query {
  account {
    id
    stores {
      edges {
        node {
          id
          name
          storeHash
          users {
              collectionInfo {
                totalItems
              }
            edges {
              node {
                id
                email
                firstName
                lastName
                locale
                lastLoginAt
                permissions
                status
                updatedAt
                apps {
                  edges {
                    node {
                      id
                      name
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
          apps {
            edges {
              node {
                id
                name
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

