TITLE: GraphQL Query with Depth of Six
DESCRIPTION: This GraphQL query illustrates a query with a depth of 6.  The fragment `CategoryFields` increases the depth by one level where used.  Each level of nesting increases the depth, which, if exceeding the limit of 16, will result in an error.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bigcommerce/docs/blob/main/docs/storefront/graphql/index.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_17

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
query {                                 // depth 0
  site {                                // depth 1
    categoryTree {                      // depth 2
      ...CategoryFields                 // depth 3
      children {                        // depth 3  
        ...CategoryFields               // depth 4
        children {                      // depth 4
          ...CategoryFields             // depth 5
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

fragment CategoryFields on CategoryTreeItem {
  name
}
```

