TITLE: Product Template GraphQL Configuration
DESCRIPTION: Example of a front matter block configuration combining product settings with a GraphQL query to fetch product variants. The query requests variant SKUs and default images for a specific product.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bigcommerce/docs/blob/main/docs/storefront/stencil/themes/context/frontmatter-reference.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
product:
  videos:
      limit: {{theme_settings.productpage_videos_count}}
  reviews:
      limit: {{theme_settings.productpage_reviews_count}}
  related_products:
      limit: {{theme_settings.productpage_related_products_count}}
  similar_by_views:
      limit: {{theme_settings.productpage_similar_by_views_count}}
gql: "query productById($productId: Int!) {
  site {
    product(entityId: $productId) {
      variants(first: 25) {
        edges {
          node {
            sku
            defaultImage {
              url(width: 1000)
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}"
```

